Package: ranemone
Title: R Interface to ANEMONE DB
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Watal M.", "Iwasaki", , "heavywatal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4718-7605"))
Description: ANEMONE DB is a database for biodiversity surveys based on
    environmental DNA metabarcoding. It is managed by Dr. Michio Kondoh,
    Ecological Integration Lab. at Tohoku University. This package
    provides an utility to analyze data from ANEMONE DB.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/heavywatal/ranemone,
